This Lambda function serves as a backend to manage and query inventory information.

Available Function is getInventory
- Without product_name: Returns list of all products with their inventory levels
- With product_name: Returns inventory details for specific product

Input Format:
{
    "function": "string",
    "parameters": [
        {
            "name": "product_name",
            "value": "string"
        }
    ]
}

Sample Request:
{
    "function": "getInventory",
    "parameters": [
        {
            "name": "product_name",
            "value": "Meow Munchies"
        }
    ]
}

Sample Response:
{
    "name": "Meow Munchies",
    "quantity": 150,
    "last_updated": "ISO-8601 date",
    "status": "in_stock|low_stock|out_of_stock",
    "reorder_level": 50
}